Individual




Sean D. Major



Mr. Sean D. Major is Executive Vice President & General Counsel at Air Products & Chemicals, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at International Mining Machinery Holdings Ltd. Mr. Major was previously employed as Secretary, Executive VP & General Counsel by Joy Global, Inc., International Counsel by Abbott Laboratories, and Assistant General Counsel & Assistant Secretary by Johnson Controls, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from DePauw University, a graduate degree from Indiana University and an MBA from Kellogg School of Management.



